      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 190,
      "message": "Questions:\nCan a DefaultServlet be in the same package as a JaxRs Servlet?   We have to make sure that there's no bad interactions. \n\nSame question about the servletPath, can a JaxRs Servlet and the DefaultServlet coexist under the same \"servletPath\"? if not we need checks for it.",
